    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by classic arcade shooters and action games, Pointblank<strong> </strong>drops you into a brutal minimalist arena where every enemy has to be taken down with just a single bullet. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick it back up, you're going to need it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Facing waves of increasingly relentless foes, use powerful augments (and precise aim) to rack up your score and survive just a little longer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adapt on the fly, achieve insane high-scores, and compete on the global leaderboards, with each encounter pushing your reflexes and accuracy to the limit. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have a single bullet: make sure every shot counts.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experiment with 20+ unique augments that help you in your runs.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive endless waves of enemies in high-intensity, brutally difficult combat.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grind for shards to unlock augment pools by killing enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb the global leaderboards and compete for the highest score worldwide.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Minimalist aesthetic with flat colors and clean visuals.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Precision-based gameplay that rewards quick reflexes and on-the-fly decisions.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
